history.content:
You could try contacting the stats department advisors, but they are under no obligation to help with this.

More generally, the solution is to wait for there to be open space in stats 140, and then drop / reenroll, filling out the SIS time conflict form then.

I am currently #8 on the STAT 140 waitlist. I am already enrolled in EECS 126. My Stat 140 lecture has a time conflict with my 126 discussion and my Stat 140 discussion has a conflict with my 126 discussion. If and when I rise to the top of the 140 waitlist, I understand that I would not be able to enroll in the class directly. Who do I contact to override the time conflict for stat 140 while enrolling from the waitlist?
history.subject: STAT 140 conflict override for waitlist
